A Class A light wine license may be issued only in:
Anne Arundel County;
Baltimore County;
Calvert County;
Caroline County;
Carroll County;
Cecil County;
Dorchester County;
Frederick County;
Garrett County;
Harford County;
Howard County;
Kent County;
Montgomery County;
Prince George's County;
Queen Anne's County;
St. Mary's County;
Somerset County;
Talbot County;
Washington County;
Wicomico County; and
Worcester County.

